</p> </div> <!-- Steps grid --> <div class="relative grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8"> <!-- Connecting line (desktop only) --> <div class="hidden md:block absolute top-10 left-[16.67%] right-[16.67%] h-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-orange via-brand-amber to-brand-orange opacity-30" aria-hidden="true"></div> <div class="relative bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-100 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300 hover:border-brand-orange/30"> <!-- Numbered circle --> <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-brand-orange flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-lg shadow-orange-200 relative z-10"> <span class="text-white font-bold text-lg">01</span> </div> <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-dark text-lg mb-3">Free Savings Analysis</h3> <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Daniel reviews your utility bills and designs a custom solar system sized for your home and energy usage. Zero cost, zero obligation.</p> </div><div class="relative bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-100 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300 hover:border-brand-orange/30"> <!-- Numbered circle --> <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-brand-orange flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-lg shadow-orange-200 relative z-10"> <span class="text-white font-bold text-lg">02</span> </div> <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-dark text-lg mb-3">Permits &amp; Installation</h3> <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Daniel coordinates permits, HOA approvals, and schedules your installation with Sunder&#39;s certified crews. Average install: 1–2 days.</p> </div><div class="relative bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-100 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300 hover:border-brand-orange/30"> <!-- Numbered circle --> <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-brand-orange flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-lg shadow-orange-200 relative z-10"> <span class="text-white font-bold text-lg">03</span> </div> <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-dark text-lg mb-3">Start Saving Immediately</h3> <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Once your utility approves interconnection, your system goes live. Watch your bill drop from day one — and lock in rates for 25 years.</p> </div> </div> <!-- CTA under steps --> <div class="text-center mt-10"> <a href="https://danielhadobas.com/sodsolarsavings" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-brand-orange text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold cta-glow">
